Manage Audio Files

Audio files can be uploaded and listen through the ConservationSpace.

 

Upload Audio File

To upload an audio file:

  1. Select the Create / Upload
  2. Select the context you want the Audio file to be uploaded

Note: You can upload the audio file in the context of a cultural object or in the context of project or any folder. Uploading an audio file in the context of another system objects means that this audio will be part of that context and the permissions on that audio will depend on this context.

 

          3. Select "Upload" option

          4. Select "Select file.." option and chose the file from you local drive

          5 "Audio" as a type will be recognized automatically if you are uploading audio file types
